{"tid":1578684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非零暴力百萬人集合?勇武本錢後盾? 民意逆轉?","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T10:34:25.000Z","uid":264071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3440dee62dfe05ccf7573b686ce0dbb7324756","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"和理非零暴力百萬人集合?勇武本錢後盾? 民意逆轉?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我好認同有巴打話要和理非零暴力百萬人再集合。</span>可能有人話有你唔出手，班鬼都幫你出手啦，但其實好似818咁，講到明和理非，邊個衝邊個就係鬼。咁最後就得翻班popo同鬼on99咁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武嘅本錢同後盾係咩?</span><br />\n我諗大家要諗一諗。如果冇和理非，淨勇武得唔得?和勇缺一不可!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民意會唔會逆轉?</span><br />\n好多風都話唔會，但無野係絕對。雖然我都覺民意唔會咁易逆轉，但<span style=\"color: red;\">你要show到出黎先得，你要show到出黎先得，你要show到出黎先得</span>，唔好成日自我沉醉。<br />\n支持勇武嘅係好多，但唔代表佢地本身係勇武。勇武夠膽企出黎，但<span style=\"color: red;\">更重要係令和理非都夠膽企出黎</span>，因為成日一開戰，和理非就會驚，特別係老一輩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近期風向就係鼓吹勇武，要勇武出曬黎，之後捉鳩曬勇武，班狗點捉你自己有眼睇，咁點解唔停一停比和理非帶路?<br />\n長期勇武其實就等於持續送頭，既然佢地每次都咁捉，就等佢地冇得捉，當佢地以為捉曬，又彈出黎吹咩，佢地一捉又彈翻入去，吹咩。等佢地自己長期神經緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個最鍾意鼓吹暴力?政府一定係其中之一，因為佢贏硬你。但唔代表唔可以暴力，不過要收放自如。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一定要再黎一次 和理非零暴力百萬人集合，咁先<span style=\"color: red;\">比全世界再睇</span>到民意。"},{"pid":"1412d06ea902179321a67da6f04347b09a4f9bdb","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d1c1bef4f980241b6376d32aeac1a48b90a1b55","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3dd1a4b180f47ca493d18fa138b9ea45ec217641","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:55:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0692919a2229d55b22ec7a42381a1ce2dd106e0b","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f84d6a5c9e060f57faccccb4e7df0d456494cf58","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:55:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"678acd667c6ff0a4d963f90c4d3a10eb60b277d5","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da750b87f11ec9980f30602e012c6da0912d0103","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1205d1a99d8b27cf9229d9e4e0bb6af9d15dd04","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d0a4abe141ae8535bc6238435656839408d4be1","tid":1578684,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ed75bcf88a36795100079ed21d03acd90af6d31","tid":1578684,"uid":124910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a28782a38c7f557be0f43aff52967a739aecad0","tid":1578684,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"百萬人行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c089ac1ef5321a98eba52baa69b015af1361953","tid":1578684,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤就係民意。<br />\n<br />\n點解政府失去民意，就係因為不斷撩交打，不斷點火頭，不斷推出政策惹起爭議。"}]}